These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-1::.
House: victorian, art-deco, wooden, cape-cod, futuristic, cottage
6 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, hedgehog, pony, snake
 1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 3. the futuristic house is on the right of the wooden house##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 5. the owner of the goat is the futuristic house##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
 7. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
 9. the cape-cod house is on the far left or far right##3
10. the wooden house is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
11. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
12. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |    3     |  4   |       5       |   6   |
| House   | cape-cod | cottage | art-deco    | victorian | wooden | futuristic |
| Pet        | cat      | snake  | hedgehog | bird | pony          | goat  |

