.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, march, july, october, june, january
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, italian, japanese, nigerian, russian
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the american is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 3. the japanese is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 4. the japanese is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 5. the nigerian is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is the italian##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 8. the russian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the japanese is on the right of the italian##1
11. the nigerian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
12. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
13. the italian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
14. the italian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4     |     5     |    6     |
| Birthday      | november  | october     | march | july    | january       | june  |
| Nationality   | russian | american | italian       | japanese | argentine | nigerian |

