.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-3::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, bongani, cain, swisher, siglo
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bus, motorbike, quad-bike, snowmobile, train
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
2. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
7. the baccarat-smoker is between the cain-smoker and the bongani-smoker##2
8. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |      3      |     4     |    5     |     6     |
| Cigar         | cain | baccarat | bongani | swisher | aristoff  | siglo    |
| Transport   | train      | motorbike  | snowmobile  | bus       | airplane | quad-bike |

