.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-4::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, fonseca, prince, aristoff, game, oliveros
The people have 6 different hobbies: camping, card-games, drawing, fishing, reading, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 2. the game-smoker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is the aristoff-smoker##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the fonseca-smoker##3
 8. the oliveros-smoker is between the person who's hobby is camping and the game-smoker##2
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
10. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |       6       |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | oliveros     | game | ritmeester        | aristoff   | prince |
| Hobby      | camping | reading | drawing  | card-games | writing | fishing       |

