.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-5::.
City: nizza, marseilles, prague, venice, boston, hamburg
There are 6 different nationalities: american, chinese, japanese, mexican, nigerian, polish
1. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to boston##2
2. the polish is on the left or right of the japanese##3
3. the nigerian is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the polish is the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the japanese is on the far right##1
6. the american is the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
8. the nigerian is on the far left##1
9. the american is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |     5     |    6     |
| City          | hamburg | boston | prague | nizza | marseilles | venice   |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | american   | chinese    | mexican | polish    | japanese |

