.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-6::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, firefighter, lawyer, project-manager, scientist
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: iris, amaryllis, bellflower, marigold, azalea, daffodil
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 2. the bartender is between the person who growsmarigold and the scientist##2
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the firefighter##1
 5. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 6. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1
 7. the bartender is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 8. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 9. the scientist is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the dancer is on the far left##1
11. the person who growsiris is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |   2    |     3     |     4      |      5       |        6        |
| Job     | dancer        | lawyer | scientist | bartender  | firefighter  | project-manager |
| Flower   | bellflower | amaryllis   | iris  | daffodil | marigold | azalea          |

