.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-3-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, soy-milk, lemonade, water, sprite
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person drinking water is the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the goldfish and the person drinking coffee##2
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |    3     |     4      |   5    |     6      |
| Pet         | hedgehog | goat      | goldfish | guinea-pig | ferret | chinchilla |
| Beverage   | coffee  | fanta | water   | sprite        | soy-milk   | lemonade |

