The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: musical, drama, disaster, horror, zombie, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
9. the person watching drama movies is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person watching disaster movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4     |      5      |       6       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | lemonade | 7up     | juice    | almond-milk | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre      | musical | zombie   | horror | disaster | drama    | time-travel       |

