 3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 6. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 8. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
11. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2   |   3    |   4    |      5      |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | punk | funk | folk | disco | d&b | blues |
| Pet    | horse     | mouse | turtle | ferret | cat         | rat       |

